<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgba(218, 226, 174, 0.15); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0.544px; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); line-height: 2em; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">许多人在春天会出现失眠、疲倦、健忘、情绪低落、好冲动、学习效率降低、睡眠不好、注意力不集中等不适症状，这些症状在春季很容易被诱发或加重。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgba(218, 226, 174, 0.15); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0.544px; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); line-height: 2em; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">今天我们来一起聊聊<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 20px;">春季心理健康！</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgba(218, 226, 174, 0.15); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0.544px; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); line-height: 2em; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 20px;"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/2n18Qa8gmEKIvzkppOLyujv67dxzfUo0mR2aJL5htBDCoQUbwmYEIkW8Cia40r1zlwiaJKSfhjFGPJpwoll8B1Kg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1" alt="图片" width="153" height="144" style="width: 153px; height: 144px;"/></span></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">具体表现为身体莫名的不舒服，不舒服的感觉经常变换位置，例如有时候食欲下降，有时候拉肚子，有时候头晕头痛，有时候还会一冷一热，甚至有时候觉得心脏不舒服，但是经医生反复检查却查不出是什么器质性疾病，这时候就应该考虑可能是由心理冲突引起的。</span></p>